===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: lĕ'ksĭkəl
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ˈleksɪkəl/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /"leksIk@l/

===Adjective===
'''lexical''' (adverb: [[lexically]])
* 1. concerning the words or [[morpheme|morphemes]] of a language.
* 2. concerning  (a.) [[lexicography]]  or  (b.) a [[lexicon]] or [[dictionary]].  Example: "Wiktionary is an essentially ''lexical'' undertaking."

